Upgrade Today - We are always working on making our Wing experience better. Get At It!

Please update your Wingstop app - you’ll be glad you did! We just fired up a new ordering feature that you’re going to love... but you’ll need this app update in order to use it. See below for details:

- You asked for it, we’re on it. Now you can choose how many of your wings you want sauced and tossed in each of your favorite flavors. Want to order a 20 piece with 10 Atomic, 5 Original Hot and 5 Lemon Pepper? No problem. A 10 piece with 3 Hickory Smoked BBQ and 7 Hawaiian? Easy. You dial up the numbers, we’ll dial up the flavor. Just update the app and you’ll be ready to GET AT IT with flavor-selecting greatness.

- Do you like typing in your credit card info at checkout? We don’t either. With this update, you can use the camera on your phone to scan in your credit or debit card.

- Need to give us a shout? With this update, now you can send us a message from the new “Contact Us” link in the nav menu.

- Now you can choose how many of your wings you want sauced and tossed in each of your favorite flavors. Want to order a 20 piece with 10 Atomic, 5 Original Hot and 5 Lemon Pepper? No problem. A 10 piece with 3 Hickory Smoked BBQ and 7 Hawaiian? Easy. You dial up the numbers, we’ll dial up the flavor. Just update the app and you’ll be ready to GET AT IT with flavor-selecting greatness.

- Do you like typing in your credit card info at checkout? We don’t either. With this update, you can use the camera on your phone to scan in your credit or debit card.

- Need to give us a shout? With this update, now you can send us a message from the new “Contact Us” link in the nav menu.

- We have a new look!
- Finding a Wingstop is easier than ever. We’ll detect your nearest location automatically so you can order even faster. You can also locate restaurants on your own by List or Map
- Need to change restaurant locations after you’ve built your order? No problem. Now you can do so on the checkout page.
- Do you have a favorite Wingstop? Now you can mark your favorite locations and we'll remember them for you.
Thanks for using the Wingstop app!  Please update to the latest version to take advantage of new features and fixes.  Get At It!

What’s new:

Completely new app, redesigned for all Wingstop lovers:

- Order wings ASAP or up to 7 days in advance with our streamlined quick-n-easy flow
- Customize your mix of iconic flavors with adjustable heat levels, rub styles and in-depth descriptions
- Deliver wings straight from the app to your doorstep
- Easily get directions and store info for any Wingstop location
- New, crisp wing imagery
